Cell["\<\
It  look like the coefficient of z^2 is growing linearly, the coefficient of \
z^3 is growing quadratically, and in general the coefficient of z^d is \
growing as n^(d-1). \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.957871309351899*^9, 
